node.text: Our Signature White Distressed Candlesticks are a team effort and go through quite a few stages before they are ready for your home. Turning, sanding, staining, painting, distressing, and finally finished off and branded with our signature "H" on the bottom. Every time you see one of our candlesticks we hope the love and care that each of our team members poured into it shines through! ❤️
